## 5) Implementation Notes for Codex (updated, with layout guidance)

### 5.1 Tech assumptions (safe defaults)
- Framework: Next.js (App Router) + React
- Styling: Tailwind (default tokens; you will replace later)
- Components: simple local components (no dependency lock-in)
- Assets: placeholders only
- Content: sourced from JSON above (single source of truth)

### 5.2 Key implementation requirements
